Re: you know how...?
by Yudan Taiteki » Sun 12.06.2009 8:49 pm I did want to point out that at least for me, "you know how..." doesn't have to lead to a negative conclusion, just an unexpected one."You know how I thought that article was going to be really difficult? Actually I finished it in one day."
